"oil-for-food" deal and there was still hope to solve the crisis
through diplomacy.
</P>
<P>
Iraq announced Thursday to immediately expel Americans in the
United Nations arms inspection teams in Iraq, which prompted the
withdrawal of the U.N. staff of the arms inspection teams.
</P>
<P>
The Security Council of the United Nations this week has
adopted a resolution and issued a presidential statement, urging
Iraq to fully comply with the relevant resolutions. 
