<TEXT>
<P>
LUSAKA, November 14 (Xinhua) -- Zambia's Anti-Corruption
Commission (ACC) launched a mobile office truck here today to
strengthen its anti-corruption campaign.
</P>
<P>
The truck will be used for community civic campaigns on the
evils and dangerous effects of corruption as well as for
enlisting and soliciting public support against the vice.
</P>
<P>
The truck, fully equipped with a public address system,
