<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Urgent: Myanmar Forms New Governing Body </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
YANGON, November 15 (Xinhua) -- Myanmar today formed the State
Peace and Development Council as its new governing body of the
country, replacing the State Law and Order Restoration Council
(SLORC), according to an official announcement this evening.
</P>
