</P>
<P>
Central committee member of the opposition United National
Independence Party (UNIP) Toyaonse Kabwe said here Friday his
party will cooperate with the local commission to facilitate
investigation into the alleged shooting of the two opposition
leaders by police if requested, according to Times of Zambia.
</P>
<P>
