<HEADLINE> 18 Ugandans Missing in Lake Accident </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, November 15 (Xinhua) -- Eighteen people supposedly
died in a lake accident yesterday in western Uganda, ''The
Monitor'' paper reported today.
</P>
<P>
