<HEADLINE> Bomb Blast Kills 4 in India </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
NEW DELHI, November 15 (Xinhua) -- Four people were killed when
some country bombs exploded in a club house in India's Orissa
state Friday evening, the local press said today.
</P>
<P>
According to police, the mishap occurred when the bombs were
being prepared in the club house.
</P>
<P>
While two persons died on the spot, the other two succumbed to
injuries in a local hospital. 
</P>
