while inaugurating a conference on "Towards SAARC Economic Union"
organized by the SAARC Chamber of Commerce and Industry here
Friday.
</P>
<P>
He said that a number of facilitation activities are being
undertaken for promoting intra-investment within the region in a
bid to help augment the quantum of investment taking place in each
other's country.  
